AngularJS is a javascript framework similar to jquery.

Advantages of angularJS
Data binding
Object scopes
Clean MVC


Angular Js directives
ng-app,ng-controller,ng-bind,ng-modal,ng-click,ng-show,ng-hide,ng-repeat

Angular Js filters
uppercase,lowercase,

Angular Js services
$https





